setsw1:     set spectral width in evolution dimension (M)

	Syntex:		setsw1(nucleus,downfieldppm, upfieldppm):offset
	Description:	sw1 is set for the given spectral window and the
			nucleus and the appropriate offset is returned.
			Referencing also done.
        
	Example:	setsw1(tn,12,0)
			setsw1(dn,235,-15):dof
			
	Related:	setsw
			setsw2     		
